   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Communication tools for young adults with autism</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For young adults with autism, technology can often make the difference between a life of isolation and a chance for a vibrant, related social learning experience.  This challenge is to raise $5,000 to buy interactive white boards for young adults in 3LPlace&apos;s new Life College. The white boards provide different ways of presenting information: through sight, touch and real time, active engagement with the material. If we have 40 donors in 30 days, we also win a spot here on Global Giving!</narrative>
  </description>
